                    <span>I am totally disappointed in this book.  I was very anxious to learn ASP.NET and I wanted to find an inexpensive book to help me get started, but the only thing this book did was frustrate me with horrible examples.  Almost every single example in the book contained an error.  Very disappointing.</span>
                  
              
